        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2019-02-27 13:56:41.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n(1 comment)\n\n1) better documentation of what is going on within the code, and 2) more unit tests around this portion.\n\n- OK, I can do that. I did that in another commit, but then I got the comment to remove it because it was cluttering. \n\n2) more unit tests around this portion\n- agreed, this class has no unit test at all and that is something we plan to do (it is just not done yet).",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "618c74f564b168b918fce59e48cc9720e7dfbe21",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 105,
          "name": "Tony Hansen",
