          "email": "tony@att.com",
          "username": "TonyLHansen"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2019-02-28 04:27:04.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nI'm not going to require the parameterization as part of this PR. Instead I created https://jira.onap.org/browse/DCAEGEN2-1299 to cover it. Please assign it to yourself. (I tried, but Jira didn't find your ID.)\n\nNote that some of the PTLs are completely blocking PRs that do not have adequate unit test coverage. During discussion at the PTL meeting, most of the PTLs considered that a good practice to follow.\n\nSo expect more push back as time goes on for changes that aren't covered by unit tests.\n\nIf you can't do the unit tests right now, then file a Jira ticket for the issue and let me know what the number is.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
